{"tid":2463710,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"薇婭1小時賣出2000多萬元新疆棉製品","createTime":"2021-03-27T02:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T04:37:53.000Z","uid":98317,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7eb9f93a766769db9c505511514ddaa0996bbf1f","tid":2463710,"uid":98317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:33:23.000Z","msg":"26日，淘寶知名主播薇婭在直播間為新疆長絨棉公益帶貨，向網友推薦來自新疆的優質棉花製品，包括毛浴巾套裝、全棉四件套以及兒童內褲等11種採用新疆棉的產品。據統計，該場公益直播1小時內約有1200萬人次在線收看，在普及宣傳新疆棉知識同時，僅1小時就幫助銷售價值約2352萬元新疆棉製品。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">當天直播結束後，銷售額接近8200萬人民幣</span></strong>，薇婭表示，希望讓大家真正感受到新疆棉的優良品質。此次直播中，11件新疆棉製品為公益直播，未收取任何費用。此前，因海外公司污蔑新疆長絨棉一事，薇婭在直播間中臨時下架兩款產品"},{"pid":"c54dd1115d3c5e856bc11877b05d155ae02fa661","tid":2463710,"uid":321002,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:34:05.000Z","msg":"嚟啲真人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b292968681a4f438938a6be21b1dfd64bfc02d24","tid":2463710,"uid":134415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:35:34.000Z","msg":"stupid nation"},{"pid":"8e326d5f524eaa48a9626bb9945faa05b90cd470","tid":2463710,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:36:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當天直播結束後，銷售額接近8200萬人民幣，薇婭表示，希望讓大家真正感受到新疆棉的優良品質。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n血棉"},{"pid":"98bfbb88652d0b13943ae60721f5c95bb3224277","tid":2463710,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T04:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn-images-1.listennotes.com/podcasts/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%89%E8%81%B2%E6%9B%B8/%E9%86%9C%E9%99%8B%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA_%E5%A5%BD%E6%9B%B8%E6%8E%A8%E8%96%A6_-202009--gB5bmOT9xKQ-w8EYmPDrTkf.1400x1400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"ht